red Sicily from the Arabs. His son, also called Roger, ruled Sicily as king, presiding over a court noted for its splendour and patronage of the arts."],"variants":[{"name":"Rodger","meanings":["Variant spelling of   Roger  , in part from the surname derived from the given name in the Middle Ages."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"Oger de Cabulian was born about 1155, in Prestbury, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom as the son of Oger De Cabulian. He had at least 1 son. He died in 1180, at the age of 26."},"et":{"ABT 1155–1180":"umbes 1155–1180","1155–1180":"1155–1180","1162–Male":"1162–Surnud","1180–1205":"1180–1205","1135–Male":"1135–Surnud","1205":"1205","ABT 1155":"umbes 1155","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","Adlington,Prestbury,Cheshire,England":"Prestbury, Cheshire, Inglismaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"ABT 1155–1180":"noin 1155–1180","1155–1180":"1155–1180","1162–Male":"1162–Kuollut","1180–1205":"1180–1205","1135–Male":"1135–Kuollut","1205":"1205","ABT 1155":"noin 1155","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","Adlington,Prestbury,Cheshire,England":"Prestbury, Cheshire, Englanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"ABT 1155–1180":"environ 1155–1180","1155–1180":"1155–1180","1162–Male":"1162–Décédé","1180–1205":"1180–1205","1135–Male":"1135–Décédé","1205":"1205","ABT 1155":"environ 1155","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","Adlington,Prestbury,Cheshire,England":"Prestbury, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Oger de Cabulian est né environ 1155, à Prestbury, Cheshire, Angleterre, Royaume-Uni, fils de Oger De Cabulian. Il a eu au moins 1 fils. Il est décédé en 1180, à l’âge de 26 ans."},"de":{"ABT 1155–1180":"um 1155–1180","1155–1180":"1155–1180","1162–Male":"1162–Verstorben","1180–1205":"1180–1205","1135–Male":"1135–Verstorben","1205":"1205","ABT 1155":"um 1155","1135":"1135","1155":"1155","1162":"1162","1180":"1180","Adlington,Prestbury,Cheshire,England":"Prestbury, Cheshire, England, United Kingdom","life